le.com%2Farticle%2Fhollywood-discovers-an%2F4573&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APass+by+catastrophe\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Gates, Anita (August 21, 1998). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9B04E0DA133DF932A1575BC0A96E958260\">\"Film review: A Novel Way to Get All A's\"</a>. <i>New York Times</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">12 May</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Film+review%3A+A+Novel+Way+to+Get+All+A%27s&amp;rft.date=1998-08-21&amp;rft.aulast=Gates&amp;rft.aufirst=Anita&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fmovie%2Freview%3Fres%3D9B04E0DA133DF932A1575BC0A96E958260&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APass+by+catastrophe\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/160467/The-Curve/overview\">\"The Curve (1998)\"</a>. <i>New York Times</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">12 May</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=The+Curve+%281998%29&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fmovies%2Fmovie%2F160467%2FThe-Curve%2Foverview&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APass+by+catastrophe\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"d